(5133, 304, 'ai_fr_description', 'Most small to mid-sized businesses are in an abusive relationship with their \"IT partner\". From not being there when you need them, to not caring about your business, to point-blank lying about costs, and everything in between.\r\n\r\nOh, and let\'s not forget the lack of expertise, making and breaking promises to you,<strong>because they simply don\'t have what it takes to make IT work</strong>. You may find that you\'re spending the bulk of your time dealing with one issue or the other  time that should have been spent growing your business. Things don\'t have to be that way for your small to mid-sized business.\r\n\r\nAt Dwyer IT, we\'ve taken a hard look at the traditional fails in the IT industry and<strong>developed a model that does things 100% differently.</strong>Why? because running a growing business doesn\'t have to be a sentence to a life of archaic IT solutions and crappy internet! Hear us out...'),
(5134, 304, '_ai_fr_description', 'field_6482ea4795c6f'),
(5135, 304, 'ai_fr_image', '287'),
