(5137, 304, 'ai_sr_heading', 'The Dwyer IT story...'),
(5138, 304, '_ai_sr_heading', 'field_6482ea9895c71'),
(5139, 304, 'ai_sr_description', 'Dwyer IT was founded in 2012 because we wanted to help people in a different way. We wanted to be<strong>honest about pricing, offer complete (not band-aid) solutions, and have long-term relationships with our clients</strong>. This would be the best situation for everyone involved  our clients and ourselves included.\r\n\r\nTechnology has changed a lot in the last 10 years and our business has changed too. But there are some things that have stayed the same.<strong>Our core values remain steadfast</strong>. We are happy to report that theyre just as relevant and important today as they ever were in 2012.\r\n\r\n<strong>We are strategic about helping our clients improve their operations while slashing costs.</strong>By partnering up with top-tier technology leaders, we get the best deals for our clients. Dwyer IT has the expertise to deliver solutions that meet and even exceed our clients\' expectations. We\'re also the best company to talk to when you need help with integrating or implementing systems into your business.'),
(5140, 304, '_ai_sr_description', 'field_6482eace95c72'),
