(6091, 388, 'modules_4_description', '<p class=\"paragraph feature-v3\">When most people think of crime in the construction industry, they think of petty theft or vandalism. However, because the workforce is mobile, spread out, and has high personnel turnover, the construction industry has become a prime target for cybercriminals.</p>\r\nA<a href=\"https://www.scarlettculture.com/it-audit-services/cybersecurity-assessments\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">cybersecurity assessment</a>will help you understand the risks your business faces and how to eliminate them to protect your company, your employees and your clients.'),
