(7244, 417, '_modules_2_heading', 'field_6481f9d76c787'),
(7245, 417, 'modules_2_description', '<p class=\"paragraph feature-v3\">Outsourcing IT allows your firm to essentially hire an entire IT team with different specialties and expertise to solve all your technology problems. This means that regardless of the technology problem that may arise, a dedicated IT member from our reputable IT firm will be able to quickly and efficiently help. Dwyer IT is available 24/7/365 and can tailor solutions to fit the needs of individual clients.</p>'),
