(7262, 417, '_modules_3_heading', 'field_6481f9d76c787'),
(7263, 417, 'modules_3_description', '<p class=\"paragraph feature-v3\">It may seem as though outsourcing to an IT company would be cost prohibitive for many firms, especially small or medium sized firms. However, when you consider the time it would take for an employee not trained in IT to research a problem, hopefully find a solution, and attempt to fix it, the time would be better spent running your business.\r\n\r\nManaged IT companies stay on top of the latest technology trends and cyber risks; an IT company can fix the problem in a fraction of the time, without the expense of a full time IT department.</p>'),
