(7355, 417, 'modules_8_description', '<p class=\"paragraph feature-v3\">Because of the nature of construction, in that it usually consists of temporary sites spread out across various cities, a cloud-based service would be the ideal choice.\r\n\r\nCloud backup reduces the risk of cybersecurity threats and costs while allowing easier access on the go. With Dwyer IT, Office 365 migrations and licensing are simple and seamless.</p>'),
