(8322, 437, '_modules_2_heading', 'field_6481f9d76c787'),
(8323, 437, 'modules_2_description', '<p class=\"paragraph feature-v3\">Many healthcare facilities are open 24/7/365, or with extended hours from early in the morning to late at night. These urgent care and other medical facilities cannot afford an IT catastrophe that could impede the ability to care for patients, no matter what time of day. Outsourced managed IT from Dwyer IT is available all hours of the day, every day of the year, to solve IT problems such as viruses, network outages and cyber attacks.\r\n\r\nWe are a HIPAA compliant IT Company and can help your medical practice immediately restore access to patient data. This allows you to promptly treat patients, maintaining patient satisfaction and preventing lost revenue due to unnecessary treatment delays. Our 24/7/365 IT Help Desk will ensure that all technology is properly functioning, and cyber attacks are responded to in a timely fashion, which increases productivity and revenue.</p>'),
