(8414, 437, '_modules_7_heading', 'field_6481f9d76c787'),
(8415, 437, 'modules_7_description', '<p class=\"paragraph feature-v3\">With strict<a href=\"https://www.scarlettculture.com/it-services-solutions/it-solutions/enterprise-file-sync-share\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HIPAA and other compliance regulations</a>, it is imperative for healthcare providers to work with a team of compliance consulting experts that will ensure that the facility remains compliant.\r\n\r\nAt Dwyer IT, we will safeguard and monitor your firms network and security system. Our efforts will help your medical office avoid a data breach of sensitive patient medical information that could lead to legal ramifications and a ruined reputation.</p>'),
