(9026, 438, '_modules_20_tagname', 'field_6481f9c36c786'),
(9027, 438, 'modules_20_heading', 'Why hire Dwyer IT for your medical offices Healthcare IT Services?'),
(9028, 438, '_modules_20_heading', 'field_6481f9d76c787'),
(9029, 438, 'modules_20_description', '<p class=\"paragraph feature-v3\">Dwyer IT is the known and trusted source for comprehensive managed IT. It is our honor, and our passion, to serve the medical community through an all-inclusive and streamlined approach to technology. Our IT professionals are trained in the particular security requirements and compliance standards that the medical industry must hold itself to. We aim to ensure compliance, while saving your office time, money and stress.</p>\r\nA HIPAA violation can cause your medical office to suffer excessive fines, as well as negative publicity. Dwyer IT is a team of compliance experts, equipped to safeguard information protected by HIPAA through advanced IT support. We provide the industrys best healthcare IT support services.\r\n\r\nOur technology specialists are experienced, supportive and available around the clock to remedy your technology woes. We offer comprehensive services, from help desk support to proactive, all-inclusive IT packages. We believe your time and effort is better spent caring for your patients while we handle all aspects of your technology infrastructure.'),
