(9482, 452, '_modules_3_heading', 'field_6481f9d76c787'),
(9483, 452, 'modules_3_description', '<p class=\"paragraph feature-v3\">It may seem as though outsourcing to an IT Support company would be cost-prohibitive for many law firms, especially small or medium-sized law firms. However, when you consider the time it would take for an employee whose specialty is not IT to research a problem, conceivably find a solution, and attempt to fix it, it is clear that the time would be better spent practicing law.Managed IT companies stay on top of the latest technology trends and cyber risks; an IT company can solve the problem in a fraction of the time, without the expense of a full-time IT department.</p>'),
