(9501, 452, 'modules_4_description', '<p class=\"paragraph feature-v3\">Technology is constantly changing and when it is not the main focus of your organization, it becomes difficult to follow and implement the relevant changes. A full-service IT provider has the ability to evaluate and implement new technologies and will assist in all facets of your law firms organization.\r\n\r\nThis is especially important when facing constant cyber threats. The law firms quickest to adapt to technology will remain safe and thrive while other legal firms will struggle to keep up.</p>'),
