(9537, 452, 'modules_6_description', '<p class=\"paragraph feature-v3\">The law requires attorneys to keep client information confidential and therefore safe from a breach. Cyber Security is a complex realm of Information Technology. When these challenges are not handled properly, it can leave your data susceptible to breach.\r\n\r\nThe best way to keep your clients information secure and confidential is with the help of an outsourced IT support company such as Dwyer IT. We understand the risks associated with GLBA and HIPAA.</p>'),
